submitted to me,

1070
01:25:35,730 --> 01:25:38,130
not only by him,

1071
01:25:38,233 --> 01:25:41,794
but by you, the technicians.

1072
01:25:41,903 --> 01:25:44,531
Because you know
the whole technical problem.

1073
01:25:44,639 --> 01:25:46,834
Thank you very much,
