Yes?

1076
01:26:00,388 --> 01:26:03,482
<i>Your Excellence,
I'm quite happy to have heard...</i>

1077
01:26:03,591 --> 01:26:06,856
<i>that you are quite ready...</i>

1078
01:26:06,961 --> 01:26:09,293
<i>to be listening
to the senior doctors.</i>

1079
01:26:09,397 --> 01:26:13,857
Not only the senior doctors,
but the young doctors,

1080
01:26:13,968 --> 01:26:18,996
