1106
01:27:37,885 --> 01:27:40,319
<i>that concerns a doctor,</i>

1107
01:27:40,421 --> 01:27:43,584
<i>if you take off
your permanent secretary...</i>

1108
01:27:43,691 --> 01:27:46,558
<i>and if you are assistant
immediate to him,</i>

1109
01:27:46,661 --> 01:27:48,561
<i>the next man to consult...</i>

1110
01:27:48,663 --> 01:27:52,292
